text: Skywatch has three main value
propositions so the first is we have an
aggregation platform for Earth
observation data to make it simple for
anyone to use the second thing we do is
we have a platform for satellite
operators and the third thing is we have
a predictive demand analytics capability
so we take all of that data from all of
our active customers on our Marketplace
and we present that in a smart way to
these satellite operators so the
combination of all those things really
represents our value prop we've been
with AWS from very early on and you know
we were fortunate enough when you're a

all of the the features that are

image to our customers we can understand
how much compute power was used by

we're really removing the
